OL,3,CSir Alex Ferguson welcomes Pep
OL,4,CGuardiola into 1000 matches club
OL,6,FSir Alex Ferguson has congratulated
OL,7,FManchester City boss Pep Guardiola
OL,8,Fahead of his 1,000th match as a
OL,9,Fmanager.
OL,11,FGuardiola will reach the landmark when
OL,12,FManchester City host Liverpool on
OL,13,FSunday 9 November, having led the club
OL,14,Fto six Premier League Titles and
OL,15,FChampions League glory.
