OL,3,CSir Alex Ferguson welcomes Pep
OL,4,CGuardiola into 1000 matches club
OL,6,FSpeaking on behalf of the League
OL,7,FManagers Association, former
OL,8,FManchester United manager Ferguson
OL,9,Fsaid: "Pep! I am absolutely delighted
OL,10,Fto welcome you to join the prestigious
OL,11,FLMA Hall of Fame 1,000 Club.
OL,13,F"Your deep love and passion for the
OL,14,Fgame has always been so evident and
OL,15,Fyou should be very proud of the
OL,16,Findelible impact you continue to have
OL,17,Facross the global game.
