OL,3,CSir Alex Ferguson welcomes Pep
OL,4,CGuardiola into 1000 matches club
OL,6,F"Reaching 1,000 matches and achieving
OL,7,Fsuch longevity in football is a
OL,8,Flandmark that can never be
OL,9,Funderestimated and, to continue to
OL,10,Fdeliver league, Champions League and
OL,11,Fdomestic cup titles in three of
OL,12,FEurope's most competitive leagues is
OL,13,Foutstanding."
OL,15,FGuardiola, having won 715 of his 999
OL,16,Fgamers so far, started his managerial
OL,17,Fcareer at Barcelona B before moving up
OL,18,Fto the main job, and he moved to
OL,19,FManchester City in 2016 after a spell
OL,20,Fat Bayern Munich.
