OL,3,CSir Alex Ferguson welcomes Pep
OL,4,CGuardiola into 1000 matches club
OL,6,FHe said: "I am so proud to be reaching
OL,7,F1,000 games as a manager which has
OL,8,Falways been a special ambition for me."
OL,10,FLMA chief executive Richard Bevan
OL,11,Fadded: "Pep has dedicated his entire
OL,12,Fcareer to achieving excellence, driven
OL,13,Fby an unmatched will to win and a
OL,14,Fworld-renowned style.
OL,16,F"His achievements and success in
OL,17,FSpain, Germany, and England are
OL,18,Funprecedented, and his influence
OL,19,Fcontinues to shape the game for future
OL,20,Fgenerations."
