OL,6,FArsenal boss Mikel Arteta described
OL,7,FGuardiola as "the most important
OL,8,Fperson in my football career", served
OL,9,Fas Manchester City assistant for three-
OL,10,Fand-a-half years until he took over at
OL,11,FArsenal in 2019.
OL,13,FHe said: "What a number, what a
OL,14,Fcareer, what an inspiration he's been
OL,15,Fto everybody in football, I would say
OL,16,Fin sports as well and especially for
OL,17,Fme.
