OL,3,CSir Alex Ferguson welcomes Pep
OL,4,CGuardiola into 1000 matches club
OL,6,F"It's an incredible achievement, it
OL,7,Fgoes in the history of the very best
OL,8,Fand the few that could only achieve
OL,9,Fsomething like that and again, as I
OL,10,Fsaid, I think it will remain in the
OL,11,Fhistory of football for the years to
OL,12,Fcome."
OL,14,FHe added: "Well, I would be extremely
OL,15,Fhappy and proud if one day I'm able to
OL,16,Fdo what he's done in his career
OL,17,Fbecause, as you all know, he's been
OL,18,Fprobably the most important person in
OL,19,Fmy football career.
